This is a record of changes made to the raw code so that should circumstances necessetate review these files are available:
Raw code version.1.0
Issue include:
  The text "plates by joshua" is the wrong color. the text should be this color: #313647
  Second, it's too far down the page. It should be centered over the merlot line, and it isn't. The top of the text box is aligned with the top of the merlot line.
  Third, there's no buffer between the lower merlot line and the contact information text box. I didn't add any information about how big a space there should be, so that's on me but there should be a space there.
  And finally, the lower textbox for the contact information is much too tall. It needs to be narrower. 
Changes to be made:
  Title text color is changed to #313647.
  Title box is repositioned to center over the merlot line.
  Added spacing between the lower merlot line and the footer content.
  Reduced height of the contact information box for a more proportional appearance.
